summary: ...NARDA NEARING HURRICANE STRENGTH WELL OFFSHORE THE COAST OF SOUTHWESTERN MEXICO... As of 2:00 AM MST Tue Sep 23 the center of Narda was located near 15.7, -106.1 with movement W at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 990 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 70 mph.
